Set Up PI:
- Flash a new MicroSD card with RasPi OS Lite 64-bit for RasPI 3b+
- Setup with username 'car'
- Set the Hostname to carpi.local
Install Updates/Things needed:
- Things that need to be installed:
  - pip3 install adafruit-circuitpython-ads1x15
  - pip3 install Adafruit-ADS1x15
  - pip3 install adafruit-circuitpython-rfm9x
  - pip3 install adafruit-circuitpython-lsm6ds
  - pip3 install pyserial
  - sudo apt install dos2unix  # Apt is better than apt-get in general because it is newer and more convenient
- All In one Commands:
  - pip3 install adafruit-circuitpython-ads1x15 Adafruit-ADS1x15 adafruit-circuitpython-rfm9x adafruit-circuitpython-lsm6ds pyserial && sudo apt install -y dos2unix
Check if everything is running:
- sudo systemctl status transmit.service code_check.service buttons.service